overview: It's Great Britain vs Australia with the prize being the British Superbike Crown. Can Shane 'Shakey' Byrne become an historic five times British Champion; or will Australian Joshua 'Bad Boy' Brookes stand in his way? If popular pin-up boy James Ellison can stay injury-free then this international superbiker line-up is going to be one hell of a roller-coaster ride!  G
title: I, Superbiker 6: Clash of Nations
